@startuml
title Kiến trúc Backend API (hotel-management-be)

left to right direction
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam defaultTextAlignment center

actor "Frontend SPA" as FE
actor "n8n (Tự động hoá)" as N8N

cloud "HTTP(S) / JSON\nPrefix: /api/v1" as HTTP

node "Backend Server" as Server {
  package "NestJS Application" as Nest {

    package "Pipeline xử lý request" as Pipeline {
      [Middleware\n(helmet, cors)] as Middleware
      [Guards\n(JWT, Roles, Throttle)] as Guards
      [ValidationPipe\n(whitelist + transform)] as Pipe
      [Controllers\n(REST endpoints)] as Controllers
      [Services\n(Business logic)] as Services
      [Repositories\n(Prisma queries - optional)] as Repos
      [PrismaService] as Prisma
    }

    package "Hạ tầng & cấu hình" as Infra {
      [ConfigModule\n(env + validation)] as Config
      [Logger\n(Pino)] as Logger
      [ScheduleModule\n+ EventEmitter] as Scheduler
      [TransformInterceptor\n(envelope response)] as Transform
      [AllExceptionsFilter] as Exceptions
      [Swagger (dev)] as Swagger
    }
  }
}

database "PostgreSQL" as PG
cloud "Cloudinary" as Cloudinary

FE --> HTTP : Gọi API
N8N --> HTTP : Gọi API automation

HTTP --> Middleware
Middleware --> Guards
Guards --> Pipe
Pipe --> Controllers
Controllers --> Services
Services --> Repos
Repos --> Prisma
Prisma --> PG : SQL

Services --> Cloudinary : Upload (tuỳ nghiệp vụ)

Controllers --> Transform : Thành công
Controllers --> Exceptions : Lỗi / Exception
Transform --> HTTP : {statusCode, message, data, meta?, timestamp}
Exceptions --> HTTP : Phản hồi lỗi chuẩn hoá

Config ..> Services
Logger ..> Controllers
Scheduler ..> Services
Swagger ..> Controllers

note right of Pipeline
Mẫu xử lý tiêu chuẩn của 1 module:
Controller -> Service -> (Repository) -> Prisma -> PostgreSQL
end note

note right of Transform
Chuẩn hoá phản hồi thành:
{ statusCode, message, data, meta?, timestamp }
- Với phân trang: { items, meta } -> { data: items, meta }
end note

@enduml
